OL,6,F"It can be cheaper and easier for
OL,7,Fbanks and businesses (to do card
OL,8,Ftransactions), but their cost savings
OL,9,Fshouldn't be at the expense of our
OL,10,Fchoice and freedom."
OL,12,FHis proposition is unlikely to be
OL,13,Fbrought to the States Assembly until
OL,14,F2025.
